00:13:29,517 --> 00:13:30,809
‎Huh?

250
00:13:30,893 --> 00:13:35,147
(Amemiya) Mari-san is better than having something hidden and protected.

251
00:13:35,231 --> 00:13:37,608
I'm sure you're the person you want to know the truth about.

252
00:13:39,151 --> 00:13:42,279
If it was hard for Mari

253
00:13:42,363 --> 00:13:46,700
‎I think it would be better to support that with all your might.

254
00:13:48,869 --> 00:13:51,705
‎Why did you think so?

255
00:13:51,789 --> 00:13:53,791
‎Eh...was it wrong? Sorry

256
00:13:53,874 --> 00:13:55,668
‎No difference

257
00:13:55,751 --> 00:13:59,964
‎I was told no touch‎I was confused for a long time...

258
00:14:00,673 --> 00:14:04,051
‎Mr. Amemiya just told me that.

259
00:14:04,134 --> 00:14:06,303
‎I understand how I feel

260
00:14:07,012 --> 00:14:09,807
‎My feelings that even I didn't understand

261
00:14:09,890 --> 00:14:11,976
How did you know, Mr. Amemiya?

262
00:14:13,477 --> 00:14:15,437
‎I understand.

263
00:14:16,230 --> 00:14:18,399
How close do you think you were?

264
00:14:20,109 --> 00:14:21,860
‎I have no friends

265
00:14:24,822 --> 00:14:27,658
I was there all the time

266
00:14:27,741 --> 00:14:29,743
‎Yes I was

267
00:14:31,328 --> 00:14:32,830
‎I'm an idiot.

268
00:14:33,831 --> 00:14:37,793
‎Eh? No, no, no, no...

269
00:14:39,169 --> 00:14:41,213
‎Tsuka Mari

270
00:14:42,673 --> 00:14:44,758
You're seriously not alone.

271
00:14:45,676 --> 00:14:47,428
‎I won't leave you alone

272
00:14:47,511 --> 00:14:50,931
Please don't be alone all by yourself.

273
00:15:00,608 --> 00:15:03,485
(Amemiya) Well, excuse me.

274
00:15:05,154 --> 00:15:06,530
‎Mr. Amemiya

275
00:15:10,409 --> 00:15:13,078
‎You are mine⸺

276
00:15:15,122 --> 00:15:16,749
It's special

277
00:15:21,295 --> 00:15:22,922
‎Hehe

278
00:15:34,308 --> 00:15:37,728
-(Islander) It would be nice if there was a hospital on the island.-(Akari) Oh, hospital.

279
00:15:37,811 --> 00:15:40,314
(Islander) It used to be there.

280
00:15:54,370 --> 00:15:57,289
Mr. Amemiya just called me and yelled at me.

281
00:15:57,373 --> 00:15:58,707
It was bad

282
00:15:58,791 --> 00:15:59,917
‎No

283
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:03,545
It's not like I was being overprotective by looking down on the young lady.

284
00:16:04,088 --> 00:16:07,466
Akari-san, it looks so delicate, right?

285
00:16:08,467 --> 00:16:10,094
‎When a young lady's heart becomes cloudy

286
00:16:10,177 --> 00:16:13,138
Akari-san also feels it and clouds it.

287
00:16:13,222 --> 00:16:16,642
That cloudiness is also felt by voters...

288
00:16:17,601 --> 00:16:19,895
Is it like cloudy?

289
00:16:22,147 --> 00:16:24,817
‎There's someone you want to check your answers with.

290
00:16:24,900 --> 00:16:26,318
‎Match the answers?

291
00:16:27,194 --> 00:16:30,114
Is it okay to talk after that?

292
00:16:34,284 --> 00:16:36,453
Can I ask you just one thing?

293
00:16:37,996 --> 00:16:38,831
‎Okay

294
00:16:39,373 --> 00:16:40,624
‎The person who wrote that letter...

295
00:16:41,834 --> 00:16:45,421
‎Not a bereaved family‎I can confirm that.

296
00:16:46,839 --> 00:16:51,260
Niiza Dean is an only child and his parents have passed away.

297
00:16:52,302 --> 00:16:56,014
My wife and child, who divorced 20 years ago, already have a family.

298
00:16:56,765 --> 00:16:59,351
They also refused to take over the body and belongings.

299
00:17:01,645 --> 00:17:03,147
‎One more thing

300
00:17:03,230 --> 00:17:05,315
Although it has not been covered in the media

301
00:17:05,399 --> 00:17:07,693
A subsequent investigation confirmed suicide.

302
00:17:09,236 --> 00:17:13,907
There was no sign of a struggle or of being pushed down.

303
00:17:13,991 --> 00:17:18,454
A camera was filming a dance practice in a park a little far away.

304
00:17:18,537 --> 00:17:20,873
‎It was small, but it seemed to be reflected.

305
00:17:21,623 --> 00:17:26,086
The moment you lean over the fence and fall

306
00:17:27,838 --> 00:17:30,716
Later, the photographer who noticed the incident reported it.

307
00:17:34,428 --> 00:17:37,598
Once I have the answers, I'll tell you everything.

308
00:17:37,681 --> 00:17:42,269
If that clouds your daughter's mind, I'll do my best to clear it up.

309
00:17:43,228 --> 00:17:45,898
Desa, young lady, I have one suggestion...

310
00:17:45,981 --> 00:17:48,525
‎No, I have something to ask.

311
00:17:49,526 --> 00:17:52,863
Should we stop using this matter in election campaigns?

312
00:17:55,199 --> 00:17:58,452
‎Find out the intent of the letter ‎Question the responsibility of the secretary general

313
00:17:58,535 --> 00:18:01,622
Take appropriate action if necessary

314
00:18:02,206 --> 00:18:07,127
But it's for the dignity of each human life.

315
00:18:09,922 --> 00:18:12,549
‎I didn't think that at first‎

316
00:18:12,633 --> 00:18:14,885
Use anything, even that letter.

317
00:18:14,968 --> 00:18:17,679
‎He was intent on cutting down Ryusei's votes.

318
00:18:19,181 --> 00:18:20,516
However, young lady

319
00:18:20,599 --> 00:18:24,394
I've been doing this and that with you for the past month.

320
00:18:25,395 --> 00:18:27,064
I had a dream

321
00:18:27,940 --> 00:18:29,107
‎Dream?

322
00:18:35,322 --> 00:18:36,156
‎This...

323
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,366
(Igarashi) Huh?

324
00:18:38,659 --> 00:18:41,620
I also received this picture of the Galaxy Express from my father...

325
00:18:41,703 --> 00:18:44,039
Until the world is completely happy?

326
00:18:45,666 --> 00:18:47,793
My boss has been displaying it in his office for a long time.

327
00:18:47,876 --> 00:18:49,753
‎Who is this?

328
00:18:49,837 --> 00:18:52,131
‎What, you don't know?

329
00:18:52,214 --> 00:18:53,924
It's Shizu-chan

330
00:18:56,218 --> 00:18:58,637
I was hooked for a while and sent it to me often.

331
00:18:59,221 --> 00:19:01,348
How many pumpkin pictures did you get?

332
00:19:03,392 --> 00:19:05,686
I can't live like this

333
00:19:07,062 --> 00:19:10,065
But I had a dream, didn't I?

334
00:19:10,148 --> 00:19:14,153
‎This election campaign‎Maybe it's my first time.

335
00:19:14,236 --> 00:19:18,115
I think it is possible to fight in a way that lives up to these words.

336
00:19:19,992 --> 00:19:23,495
Will I be able to win? So...

337
00:19:24,121 --> 00:19:25,330
‎I don't know

338
00:19:25,873 --> 00:19:29,459
But I want to prove that I can still win

339
00:19:30,335 --> 00:19:34,173
In Dean Niiza's bag left on the roof

340
00:19:34,256 --> 00:19:36,258
‎There was a book inside.

341
00:19:36,341 --> 00:19:37,467
‎"Night on the Galaxy Express"

342
00:19:38,093 --> 00:19:39,261
‎Huh?

343
00:19:39,928 --> 00:19:42,598
I've never believed in God though.

344
00:19:43,724 --> 00:19:46,101
‎If such a thing exists

345
00:19:46,184 --> 00:19:50,189
I thought maybe he would talk to me in this way.

346
00:19:56,278 --> 00:19:58,113
-(Akari) Be careful!-(Mari) Ah, yes.

347
00:19:58,906 --> 00:20:00,407
-(Akari) Not yet.-(Mari) Oh, it's scary.

348
00:20:00,490 --> 00:20:02,159
(Akari) Haven't seen it yet

349
00:20:02,242 --> 00:20:03,201
-(Akari) I haven't seen it yet‎-(Mari) Yes.

350
00:20:03,285 --> 00:20:04,286
-(Akari) Yes, here‎-(Mari) Yes

351
00:20:04,369 --> 00:20:05,829
-(Akari) I haven't seen it yet‎-(Mari) Yes.

352
00:20:05,913 --> 00:20:07,289
‎-(Akari) Good‎-(Mari) Yes.

353
00:20:08,123 --> 00:20:10,042
-(Akari) Okay then, let's go? -(Mari) Yes

354
00:20:10,125 --> 00:20:12,336
‎(Akari) Seino!

355
00:20:12,419 --> 00:20:15,255
‎Wow~ Haha

356
00:20:16,465 --> 00:20:19,092
You can see it even in Tokyo

357
00:20:19,176 --> 00:20:23,221
Go up to a high place for 10 minutes without closing your eyes

358
00:20:23,305 --> 00:20:24,932
‎Does it really look like that?

359
00:20:25,015 --> 00:20:27,100
Yeah, they said it on the radio...

360
00:20:27,184 --> 00:20:28,060
‎Ah, shooting star!

361
00:20:28,143 --> 00:20:29,770
‎Win Win Win Win

362
00:20:31,563 --> 00:20:33,440
(Two people laughing)

363
00:20:36,151 --> 00:20:38,237
‎(Akari) Huh, I'm about to cry

364
00:20:38,320 --> 00:20:39,613
‎Huh?

365
00:20:39,696 --> 00:20:42,783
‎Why not? ‎When I see something beautiful

366
00:20:46,036 --> 00:20:47,871
‎It will be.

367
00:20:47,955 --> 00:20:49,039
‎Hey

368
00:20:52,084 --> 00:20:55,629
‎When I was a child, my parents and Ryucha...

369
00:20:56,505 --> 00:20:59,258
When I went camping with my childhood friend

370
00:20:59,967 --> 00:21:02,219
I can't sleep for some reason

371
00:21:02,302 --> 00:21:04,638
‎Sneaking out of the tent in the middle of the night

372
00:21:05,597 --> 00:21:09,601
I feel like I can see railroad tracks in the galaxy

373
00:21:10,394 --> 00:21:13,563
‎Get lost and try this

374
00:21:19,778 --> 00:21:20,988
(Ruri) Mari!

375
00:21:22,489 --> 00:21:26,493
‎Ha ha…

376
00:21:28,203 --> 00:21:32,290
Both my father and childhood friend were looking for me.

377
00:21:32,958 --> 00:21:34,626
(Mari) It's beautiful.

378
00:21:34,710 --> 00:21:36,420
(Ryusei) Yeah

379
00:21:36,503 --> 00:21:38,422
(Takaomi) Here's the problem.

380
00:21:38,505 --> 00:21:41,675
Why are galaxies so beautiful?

381
00:21:42,509 --> 00:21:45,262
‎-(Mari) Hmm, I wonder what it is‎-(Ryusei) Hey.

382
00:21:45,929 --> 00:21:47,055
(Ruri) Yes

383
00:21:47,973 --> 00:21:50,892
Because each star is beautiful

384
00:21:50,976 --> 00:21:52,436
(Takaomi) Ping pong Correct answer

385
00:21:52,519 --> 00:21:54,438
(Mari) Yeah, is that so?

386
00:21:54,521 --> 00:21:55,856
‎Look and see

387
00:21:55,939 --> 00:21:57,357
(Light) It's wonderful.

388
00:21:57,441 --> 00:21:59,443
‎Lovely parents

389
00:22:00,652 --> 00:22:02,446
Although it has changed

390
00:22:05,157 --> 00:22:08,118
5 years ago my mother passed away

391
00:22:08,660 --> 00:22:11,246
My father has become a different person.

392
00:22:12,748 --> 00:22:15,250
‎Drag down the current Prime Minister

393
00:22:15,917 --> 00:22:18,795
In order for me to take that position, I will do my best.

394
00:22:20,172 --> 00:22:22,340
‎I even got married for that reason.

395
00:22:23,925 --> 00:22:27,012
‎Iwakura‎Daughter of the Chairman of Heavy Industries

396
00:22:27,095 --> 00:22:31,683
She is the niece of a former prime minister, and many of her relatives are politicians.

397
00:22:32,934 --> 00:22:35,270
‎It's completely a political marriage.

398
00:22:38,231 --> 00:22:43,153
Why do you want to be like that, Prime Minister?

399
00:22:43,236 --> 00:22:44,363
‎Huh?

400
00:22:45,822 --> 00:22:47,866
Is there something?

401
00:22:47,949 --> 00:22:51,119
‎What I want to do when I become Prime Minister

402
00:22:53,205 --> 00:22:55,499
I had never thought about it

403
00:22:56,375 --> 00:22:59,211
I guess I'm obsessed with power.

404
00:23:02,964 --> 00:23:04,174
Hey Mari-chan

405
00:23:05,884 --> 00:23:06,968
‎Yes

406
00:23:08,095 --> 00:23:09,554
‎That letter

407
00:23:11,431 --> 00:23:13,058
‎Are you going to stop using it?

408
00:23:14,059 --> 00:23:15,185
‎Huh?

409
00:23:15,268 --> 00:23:17,771
‎What Mari-chan is worried about

410
00:23:19,022 --> 00:23:24,111
Who wrote it, what they thought, and why?

411
00:23:24,694 --> 00:23:26,488
‎What my father did

412
00:23:28,323 --> 00:23:30,283
‎If you don't like it

413
00:23:30,867 --> 00:23:34,454
I'll investigate with you and accept it.

414
00:23:36,748 --> 00:23:40,669
But I use it to win

415
00:23:42,003 --> 00:23:43,088
‎Are you going to stop?

416
00:23:46,258 --> 00:23:48,552
Same thing for Mr. Igarashi.

417
00:23:48,635 --> 00:23:49,970
‎That's right

418
00:23:50,512 --> 00:23:54,558
But I couldn't reply on the spot.

419
00:23:55,308 --> 00:23:59,354
‎Does Mari-chan want to use it?

420
00:24:01,398 --> 00:24:04,484
I've been putting it off for so long

421
00:24:06,945 --> 00:24:09,990
‎For Akari-san ‎I cut up that tanka.

422
00:24:14,995 --> 00:24:19,166
‎I've been obsessed with it every day so far.

423
00:24:20,250 --> 00:24:21,376
It's fun

424
00:24:23,628 --> 00:24:26,089
‎Fun and fun

425
00:24:27,174 --> 00:24:28,091
‎Beautiful things

426
00:24:29,176 --> 00:24:31,178
‎Something so beautiful that it brings tears to my eyes

427
00:24:32,262 --> 00:24:35,473
‎I've seen a lot of things.

428
00:24:44,441 --> 00:24:45,650
‎So...

429
00:24:47,402 --> 00:24:48,570
(Light) Just like that...

430
00:24:50,280 --> 00:24:52,616
‎Why don't you just go?

431
00:24:52,699 --> 00:24:53,700
‎Huh?

432
00:24:54,326 --> 00:24:57,704
‎Enthusiastic and fun

433
00:24:59,039 --> 00:25:00,624
‎Stay clean

434
00:25:02,125 --> 00:25:03,460
‎Until the end

435
00:25:06,129 --> 00:25:07,380
‎That's it...

436
00:25:10,926 --> 00:25:12,219
‎That's it...

437
00:25:13,929 --> 00:25:15,805
Will it be allowed?

438
00:25:18,475 --> 00:25:23,021
‎It's like a dream

439
00:25:27,150 --> 00:25:28,401
‎It's not allowed.

440
00:25:32,822 --> 00:25:36,660
‎That's why we change.

441
00:25:42,999 --> 00:25:44,167
‎Yes

442
00:25:44,251 --> 00:25:46,419
(Two people laughing)

443
00:25:46,503 --> 00:25:48,296
‎(Fireflies) This is so scary, I feel like crying.

444
00:25:48,380 --> 00:25:50,548
-(Akari) I see!-(Firefly) That's amazing.

445
00:25:51,049 --> 00:25:54,094
‎-(Igarashi) Huh... hah... ‎-(Hotaru) Awesome

446
00:25:54,177 --> 00:25:56,888
-(Mari) Oh, Mr. Igarashi‎-(Akari) Hahahaha...

447
00:25:56,972 --> 00:26:02,102
(Igarashi) Huh… hah…

448
00:26:02,185 --> 00:26:03,979
‎Huh...

449
00:26:04,062 --> 00:26:06,523
(Akari) Hahaha...

450
00:26:06,606 --> 00:26:07,941
‎Mr. Igarashi

451
00:26:09,526 --> 00:26:12,570
Let's prove it and show it to you

452
00:26:13,238 --> 00:26:14,114
‎To the boss?

453
00:26:14,197 --> 00:26:15,699
‎To the world

454
00:26:15,782 --> 00:26:19,119
‎Hahahaha… Good

455
00:26:19,202 --> 00:26:20,245
(Firefly) Ah, shooting star

456
00:26:20,328 --> 00:26:24,916
(Mari/Akari) Winning Winning Winning…!

457
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:27,043
‎(Akari) Wait a minute‎Isn't it becoming "Sentou"?

458
00:26:27,127 --> 00:26:29,671
(Everyone laughs)

459
00:26:35,218 --> 00:26:36,845
(Hotaru/Igarashi) Oh~

460
00:26:55,739 --> 00:26:58,325
(Igarashi) Yes Ryusei 23.3 points

461
00:26:58,408 --> 00:27:02,078
Kazama 14.2 points Fujisato 8.1 points

462
00:27:02,162 --> 00:27:03,496
Who is Fujisato-san?

463
00:27:03,580 --> 00:27:05,415
‎Candidate recommended by the Socialist Labor Party

464
00:27:05,498 --> 00:27:07,667
-(Hotaru) It's strong after all.-(Mari) Yeah.

465
00:27:07,751 --> 00:27:08,585
What about Akari?

466
00:27:09,294 --> 00:27:11,212
‎What a 4th place

467
00:27:12,047 --> 00:27:14,215
‎5.4 points

468
00:27:14,299 --> 00:27:15,925
(Akari) Huh? Is it low? Is it expensive?

469
00:27:16,009 --> 00:27:17,093
‎Well, that's low.

470
00:27:17,177 --> 00:27:19,095
‎Dada Dada... It's okay.

471
00:27:19,179 --> 00:27:20,638
‎Here, here, here... It's from here!

472
00:27:20,722 --> 00:27:23,892
‎Mari-chan, yes, take a deep breath‎Yes, inhale~

473
00:27:23,975 --> 00:27:27,729
‎No, it's just as the young lady said‎The real thing starts from here.

474
00:27:27,812 --> 00:27:31,858
‎The total points of the top 4 people is 51

475
00:27:31,941 --> 00:27:34,402
‎5th place and below ‎approximately 2 points total

476
00:27:34,486 --> 00:27:35,320
‎In other words⸺

477
00:27:35,904 --> 00:27:41,576
Approximately 47% of respondents have not yet decided where to vote.

478
00:27:41,660 --> 00:27:43,411
‎There are floating votes.

479
00:27:43,495 --> 00:27:45,830
‎Situation survey 3 days before the notification date

480
00:27:45,914 --> 00:27:50,085
‎Ryusei got 21.4 points ‎Kazama got 8.6

481
00:27:50,168 --> 00:27:51,002
‎Huh?

482
00:27:51,086 --> 00:27:54,756
Yes, the growth of meteors is slow, and Kazama has momentum.

483
00:27:55,924 --> 00:27:58,885
I can see Shizu-chan's nails snapping.

484
00:27:58,968 --> 00:27:59,969
‎Claw snap?

485
00:28:00,053 --> 00:28:01,763
‎Huh? Haven't you noticed?

486
00:28:01,846 --> 00:28:04,682
When he gets upset, he doesn't show it on his face, but

487
00:28:04,766 --> 00:28:06,434
‎In this way...

488
00:28:06,518 --> 00:28:07,602
(sound of snapping nails)

489
00:28:07,685 --> 00:28:09,562
‎I didn't realize it

490
00:28:09,646 --> 00:28:12,190
(Igarashi) Uchiha 3.1 to 5.4

491
00:28:12,273 --> 00:28:14,734
‎Increased by 2.3 in 1 week

492
00:28:14,818 --> 00:28:16,736
‎It seems like a small number, but

493
00:28:16,820 --> 00:28:20,949
‎The important thing is Ryusei Kazama‎In terms of growth including organizational votes

494
00:28:21,032 --> 00:28:22,617
‎This is all floating votes

495
00:28:23,660 --> 00:28:27,080
‎You could say that this created a breeze.

496
00:28:27,163 --> 00:28:30,125
At this rate, continue collecting floating votes.

497
00:28:30,208 --> 00:28:33,628
‎Furthermore, with this result as a weapon, ‎I will go and collect the big organization ticket.

498
00:28:34,546 --> 00:28:38,341
Now that I'm in 4th place, I might be able to move mountains.

499
00:28:38,425 --> 00:28:40,802
‎Sermon to Buddha

500
00:28:40,885 --> 00:28:44,097
‎Large organizations and companies that may be able to support you

501
00:28:44,180 --> 00:28:46,182
‎Already the Democratic Party and the Socialist Labor Party⸺

502
00:28:46,266 --> 00:28:48,143
I guess he's being held back by the Kazama camp.

503
00:28:48,226 --> 00:28:51,104
(Igarashi) Yes, that's why I use this.

504
00:28:51,187 --> 00:28:52,105
